text: Seed of Chucky is a 2004 American comedy slasher movie. It is the fifth installment of the Child's Play series, and sequel to 1998's Bride of Chucky. The movie was written and directed by Don Mancini, who created the series. The movie, shot in Romania, continues the series' evolution from horror to a horror-comedy. It was the last Child's Play movie to be released in theaters, with all future installments to be released directly to DVD. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * * Category:2004 comedy movies Category:2004 horror movies Category:Child's Play movies Category:British comedy movies Category:British horror movies Category:Romanian comedy movies Category:Romanian horror movies Category:American comedy movies Category:American horror movies Category:Movies directed by Don Mancini
